[
  {
    "startTime": 3.362,
    "endTime": 4.195,
    "text": "Hi there."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 4.195,
    "endTime": 5.776,
    "text": "If you're a busy working guy like me,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 5.776,
    "endTime": 7.542,
    "text": "you don't always have time to cook."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 7.542,
    "endTime": 9.212,
    "text": "So rather than go grocery shopping,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 9.212,
    "endTime": 12.9,
    "text": "you rely solely on what's already in your kitchen."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 12.9,
    "endTime": 13.932,
    "text": "Let's figure it out this week on"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 13.932,
    "endTime": 15.551,
    "text": "Technically a Meal."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 15.551,
    "endTime": 19.718,
    "text": "(bright music)"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 24.197,
    "endTime": 27.709,
    "text": "As per usual, it's 2 p.m., I haven't done anything today,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 27.709,
    "endTime": 29.666,
    "text": "and I have no idea what's in here."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 29.667,
    "endTime": 31.5,
    "text": "Let's give her a spin."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 36.1,
    "endTime": 39.768,
    "text": "Okay, I thought there'd be..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 39.768,
    "endTime": 41.517,
    "text": "It was kinda slim pickings, but I think we came up"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 41.517,
    "endTime": 43.131,
    "text": "with something pretty good."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 43.131,
    "endTime": 45.741,
    "text": "First off, we have ketchup, some hot sauce,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 45.741,
    "endTime": 48.13,
    "text": "a quarter container of parmesan cheese,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 48.13,
    "endTime": 49.6,
    "text": "some olives, some eggs,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 49.6,
    "endTime": 51.77,
    "text": "a second, older bottle of ketchup,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 51.77,
    "endTime": 53.919000000000004,
    "text": "an avocado, some soup,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 53.919,
    "endTime": 56.919,
    "text": "and leftover lo mein noodles that..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 59.844,
    "endTime": 61.164,
    "text": "that are bad."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 61.164,
    "endTime": 62.414,
    "text": "These went bad."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 64.66,
    "endTime": 66.24799999999999,
    "text": "That really sucks."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 66.248,
    "endTime": 67.62,
    "text": "That was gonna, that was gonna be, like,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 67.62,
    "endTime": 69.37,
    "text": "a big part of it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 70.86,
    "endTime": 73.351,
    "text": "That was sort of a central, but--"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 73.351,
    "endTime": 76.679,
    "text": "A couple of bites of what seems to be spaghetti."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 76.679,
    "endTime": 80.846,
    "text": "So, the plan is, we're just gonna put it together..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 83.5,
    "endTime": 84.304,
    "text": "and we're gonna heat it up."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 84.305,
    "endTime": 86.34,
    "text": "We're gonna heat it up and we're gonna put it together."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 86.34,
    "endTime": 90.47800000000001,
    "text": "We're gonna put it together and we're gonna heat it up."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 90.478,
    "endTime": 91.31099999999999,
    "text": "Yeah."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 92.161,
    "endTime": 94.751,
    "text": "So I just realized these eggs are actually expired,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 94.751,
    "endTime": 97.55000000000001,
    "text": "but not by a lot, so there's an actual way to tell"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 97.55,
    "endTime": 99.227,
    "text": "whether an egg is old."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 99.227,
    "endTime": 100.554,
    "text": "There's an egg test."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 100.554,
    "endTime": 103.34400000000001,
    "text": "So let's just get started on that."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 103.344,
    "endTime": 105.92599999999999,
    "text": "If an egg sinks in the water..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 108.429,
    "endTime": 112.596,
    "text": "If your egg sinks in water, then it is good to go!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 116.31,
    "endTime": 118.727,
    "text": "Maybe easier with one hand..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 120.36,
    "endTime": 121.31099999999999,
    "text": "Sometimes it doesn't wanna sink,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 121.311,
    "endTime": 123.72800000000001,
    "text": "and you have to make it sink."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 125.62,
    "endTime": 129.85,
    "text": "If your egg sinks in water, then it's good to go!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 129.85,
    "endTime": 131.79999999999998,
    "text": "Now, the trick with an avocado is--"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 131.8,
    "endTime": 134.292,
    "text": "(metallic clanging)"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 134.292,
    "endTime": 135.36,
    "text": "This is--"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 135.36,
    "endTime": 136.32700000000003,
    "text": "(banging)"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 136.327,
    "endTime": 137.577,
    "text": "a literal rock?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 138.431,
    "endTime": 142.19,
    "text": "So even if the egg is a little old, it looks fine to me."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 142.19,
    "endTime": 144.518,
    "text": "And don't forget to heat up your spaghetti in a pan"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 144.518,
    "endTime": 146.758,
    "text": "to make you feel like you're actually cooking."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 146.758,
    "endTime": 148.435,
    "text": "So I'm gonna give this a little minute"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 148.435,
    "endTime": 149.743,
    "text": "and check in on my soup, which is heating up"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 149.743,
    "endTime": 152.29,
    "text": "in the microwave for a little appetizer."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 152.29,
    "endTime": 154.112,
    "text": "(laughs)"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 156.53,
    "endTime": 159.25,
    "text": "(microwave beeps)"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 159.25,
    "endTime": 159.858,
    "text": "Whoa!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 159.858,
    "endTime": 161.397,
    "text": "Here we go."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 161.397,
    "endTime": 164.814,
    "text": "Oh man, where are we, a fancy restaurant?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 166.361,
    "endTime": 168.25099999999998,
    "text": "That's salsa."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 168.252,
    "endTime": 169.899,
    "text": "Ugh."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 169.899,
    "endTime": 172.506,
    "text": "Soup looks like salsa."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 172.506,
    "endTime": 174.589,
    "text": "Alright, let's check back in on these eggs."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 174.589,
    "endTime": 177.23,
    "text": "Oh, cool, this is done, great."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 177.23,
    "endTime": 179.606,
    "text": "And now it's time to put it all together."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 179.606,
    "endTime": 183.773,
    "text": "(lively music)"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 184.731,
    "endTime": 185.845,
    "text": "Aw, shit."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 185.845,
    "endTime": 188.915,
    "text": "I'll mix up the ketchup and the hot sauce,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 188.915,
    "endTime": 191.248,
    "text": "and do a little bit of that."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 193.112,
    "endTime": 194.305,
    "text": "Oh, that's nice."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 194.305,
    "endTime": 195.138,
    "text": "And there we have it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 195.138,
    "endTime": 196.16,
    "text": "This is our dish."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 196.16,
    "endTime": 197.756,
    "text": "This is spaghetti,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 197.756,
    "endTime": 199.923,
    "text": "this is hot sauce..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 201.71,
    "endTime": 203.877,
    "text": "Hot ketchup egg spaghetti."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 205.17,
    "endTime": 206.719,
    "text": "Hot ketchup egg spaghetti."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 206.719,
    "endTime": 209.192,
    "text": "I'm gonna check real quick that I don't have a"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 209.193,
    "endTime": 211.526,
    "text": "coupon on Postmates."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 213.45,
    "endTime": 214.45,
    "text": "And I don't."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 215.541,
    "endTime": 216.624,
    "text": "There you go!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 218.491,
    "endTime": 220.991,
    "text": "And that's Technically a Meal."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 223.551,
    "endTime": 225.718,
    "text": "(retches)"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 229.48,
    "endTime": 231.397,
    "text": "Ugh, the eggs were bad."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 233.468,
    "endTime": 234.795,
    "text": "Hi, it's Zack from CollegeHumor."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 234.795,
    "endTime": 235.73899999999998,
    "text": "Thanks for watching."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 235.74,
    "endTime": 237.67000000000002,
    "text": "You can click here to suscribe,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 237.67,
    "endTime": 239.7,
    "text": "or you can click over here for something else fun."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 239.7,
    "endTime": 241.35299999999998,
    "text": "You can also click here if you want to feed me clicks."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 241.354,
    "endTime": 242.187,
    "text": "I like 'em."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 242.187,
    "endTime": 246.686,
    "text": "(chomps)"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 246.686,
    "endTime": 247.686,
    "text": "Mmm, clicks."
  }
]